# README

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/beau-ryan/MyCodePortfolio2.git
cd MyCodePortfolio2

# Quick setup (Windows)
.\Platforms\windows\powershell\menu.ps1

# Quick setup (Linux/macOS)
./Platforms/unix/linux/setup.sh
```

